name: Chaos Of Solus
description: Chaos Of Solus represents my journey as an artist so far. More than often creating alone presented with the chaos of the blank page, the chaos of software and hardware limitations, and the chaos of releasing this work to the world. Once all 10 editions are collected, a random draw will be held. The selected collector shall receive the full version as it was intended in 4k 60fps 5min in length. Which can be viewed here https://zeroalphadesign.myportfolio.com/nfts
